title: Feeling Like Ourselves Again
description:
Tasia shares her vacation plans, opens up about coming off of antidepressants, and reflects on the personal growth she's had in the past few years. Camo dives into their goals for future and the two of them talk about their evolving views on friendship.
Go to TalkSpace.com and use promo code UNFAZED for $100 off your first month!
